## Data Flow

### User Registration Flow
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant API
    participant Twilio
    participant Firebase
    participant Firestore

    User->>Frontend: Enter phone, name, role
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/auth/send-otp
    API->>Semaphore/Twilio: Send SMS with OTP
    Semaphore/Twilio->>User: SMS with verification code
    API->>PostgreSQL: Store verification attempt + rate limit
    API-->>Frontend: OTP sent confirmation
    
    User->>Frontend: Enter OTP + PIN
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/auth/verify-otp
    API->>PostgreSQL: Validate OTP + rate limits
    API->>Supabase: Create user account
    API->>PostgreSQL: Store user profile with RLS
    API->>PostgreSQL: Log security events
    API-->>Frontend: Registration success + JWT
    Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to role-based dashboard
```

### Real-time Tracking Flow
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Rider
    participant App
    participant API
    participant Firestore
    participant Dispatcher

    loop Every 10 seconds
        Rider->>App: GPS location update
        App->>API: POST /api/tracking/update
        API->>PostgreSQL: Update rider location with RLS
        PostgreSQL-->>Dispatcher: Real-time update via Supabase
        Dispatcher->>Dispatcher: Update map view
    end
```

